<br />
- The Thestran Web Quests are now open for players to explore. Players may begin by speaking to Grom Vermach in Halgarad, Preceptor Indradi in Leth Nurae, War Master Trabrand Silvereye in Bordinar’s Cleft, or Investigator Trenkle in Tursh. <br />
<br />
